19 Section 3-8-101. This act shall be known and may be cited as
20 the “Terry Peach North Canadian Watershed Water Restoration Act”.
21 SECTION 2. AMENDATORY Section 2, Chapter 372, O.S.L.
22 2023 (27A O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 3-8-102), is amended to read as
23 follows:
